{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "梁斗（即文士）轻松化解钟无离、柳有孔的联手攻击，武功之高令萧秋水惊叹。权力帮的一洞神魔左常生和神拳天魔盛江北出现。梁斗与盛江北展开激烈拳术比试，以博大精深的百家拳法令盛江北甘拜下风。左常生突袭以铜钹暗算梁斗，梁斗以闪电般的手法化解。随后屈寒山偕康出渔、康劫生赶到，伪装为正派侠士，打落盛江北四颗牙齿以取信梁斗，又以古深禅师来访为由将梁斗骗走，留下萧秋水孤立无援。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“不要冲动！”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“请不要动手。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“最好不要打架！”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“别担心，他打不着我的。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“原来阁下便是钟壹窟钟无离先生，怎么鼻尖少了一块肉……”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“怎么出手这么狠！”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_shi",
      "speaker_name": "文士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好了吧，我们又不是卖药的，不必耍猴戏给人看！”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“住手！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“盛老师何必动这么大的火气，这位朋友不懂功夫！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“不会武功就不能说话？那天下人不是十之八九都成了哑巴？”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你要为这人出头？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“出头不敢当。你只要也掉四颗门牙，那此事就算了。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“兔崽子，有种你来敲掉我的牙！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“我不是牙医，也不是兔子，”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“只要盛老师答应以后不要随便敲掉别人的牙齿，这个歉我就代你向那位朋友致意就是了。”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“你……你拳法比我还杂！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“旁门杂技，比不上盛老师的意深形简，承让，承让！”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_chang_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "左常生",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“闻说梁斗梁大侠见识广博，武学渊源，而今一见，所说无讹。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“盛老拳师来了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“盛江北不好对付呀，也不知梁大侠……”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“废话！梁大侠还打发不了这种贪图权势的人么？！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“果然是气吞丹霞！果然是大侠梁斗！我这才踏入广东，梁兄已大显身手！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“原来是屈兄，暖，还有康先生光临广东，有失远迎，失敬失敬！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“怎么先前未通知我一声，我和广东五虎去接你！”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这次临行匆匆，未及通知，实感惭愧。据悉广西五友也来广东了，不知……”",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“此事确然，他们广州十虎，每年一聚，这次会面地点就在高要。只不知连劳山康先生也大驾光临……”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这是小儿劫生，拜见梁大侠，他原是这位萧少侠的知友，我们此番来广，亦为救这萧少侠而来的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“原来这位便是萧少侠，我与他大哥有一面之缘，与他却未曾谋面，但见他为人所制，仍气宇不凡，想权力帮作恶多端，实难容他们公开胡作非为，才插手此事，却不知……不知康先生乃为此事而来的！康先生德高望重，仍为武林后辈之事如此操心，实是武林之幸。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“大侠客气！多年来为百姓仗义抱不平的，还不就是梁大侠仍孜孜不倦！”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“只不过却越帮越忙，伤了无辜旁人。”",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“谁伤了人？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“就是这人，打掉了一名观看者的四颗门牙！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“你……”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“梁大侠，有你我在，权力帮岂能横行！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“这人打脱别人四颗牙齿，而今也给人打脱了四颗，真是报应不爽。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“屈兄好快的身手，武当山一别后，这次又叫我好生开了眼界！”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这里的事，就交给兄弟好了，梁大侠最好还是跟康先生走一趟。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“什么事？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“古深禅师来了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“嵩山古深？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“正是古深。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“他怎么来了广东？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“他先到广西，我已接待他几天了；而今他到了广东，论地主之谊，我看梁大侠还是去一趟的好。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“他来了，我自然该去。只是，这里事情……”",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这里我可代梁大侠料理。”",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“有屈兄在此，我就放心了。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“古深禅师现在何处？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“就在七星岩阿坡岩附近。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好，我这就去。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_dou",
      "speaker_name": "梁斗",
      "listener": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "text": "“这人的穴道要先解除，他憋久了。”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qu_han_shan",
      "speaker_name": "屈寒山",
      "listener": "char_liang_dou",
      "text": "“这个自然，萧家老三，本是老友之子，我不帮他帮谁？！而且有我屈寒山，又有谁敢动他一根汗毛！何况还有梁大侠说过的金言！”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2
    }
  ],
